# Documentation Conventions

## Bilingual Structure

All documentation exists in two versions:
- `filename.md` — Russian (primary)
- `filename.en.md` — English

When editing docs, update both language versions.

## Tutorial Structure (docs/)

Lessons are numbered sequentially: `01-introduction.md`, `02-digital-twin.md`, etc.
Each has an index file: `docs/index.md` / `docs/index.en.md`.

## README

- `README.md` — Russian, primary
- `README.en.md` — English

## Audit Files

- `audit.md`, `audit_cto.md`, `rax_audit.md` — project analysis documents
- `GEMINI.md` — AI-generated architecture overview
- `pub.md` — release notes
